{"tid":1160942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王毅批評美國打壓中國企業","createTime":"2019-05-18T20:31:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-19T09:27:38.000Z","uid":7828,"like":2,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc13c5fc04a617354b029f73ddcea4439029fdc","tid":1160942,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T20:31:44.000Z","msg":"外長王毅與美國國務卿蓬佩奧通電話。<br />\n<br />\n王毅指，美方近期在多個方面的言行損害中方利益，包括通過政治手段，打壓中國企業的正常經營，中方對此堅決反對，敦促美方不要走得太遠，應當盡快改弦更張，避免中美關係進一步受損。<br />\n<br />\n王毅重申，中方一貫主張並願意通過談判磋商，解決經貿分歧，但談判應該是平等，在任何談判中，中方必須維護國家的正當利益，捍衛國際關係基本準則。<br />\n<br />\n王毅和蓬佩奧在通話中亦談到台灣問題。王毅敦促美方恪守一個中國原則，和中美三個聯合公報，慎重處理涉台問題。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=348472\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348472&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2fhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=c890ce23\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D348472&h=a8db11fa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=348472</a>"},{"pid":"0caf716cd2609599a0c3ddbb45e81ec45eb6f122","tid":1160942,"uid":3063,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T20:32:28.000Z","msg":"屌啦星<br />\n又話不怕打"},{"pid":"5c464788032ad8174d654b90f0ef61b5e18f7c31","tid":1160942,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T20:40:33.000Z","msg":"中國發動口水戰反制美帝貿易戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20f90d5a4eeae9591a8c31943a6cef28285e7780","tid":1160942,"uid":22553,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T20:48:30.000Z","msg":"人地壓你，仲成隻狗咁乞人要貨？咪唔好運貨去美國囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c2379292de27381619ab4c8cf2db7d6a95ed75d","tid":1160942,"uid":65984,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T21:16:48.000Z","msg":"擺明架啦, 吹